---
title: Easy King Prawn and Veggie 'Nduja Baked Paella with Cheese, Peas and Oven-Ready Garlic Baguettes
description: Deliciously easy to cook, it only takes 3 steps to put this Easy King Prawn and Veggie 'Nduja Baked Paella on the table. Combine our chef-approved shortcuts and simple instructions to make a restaurant quality dinner that's as easy as 1-2-3!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y24_R38_W31_UK_SRC19563-5_Main_low-e08d45dd.jpg
